text: "Can't Catch Me Now" is a song by American singer-songwriter Olivia Rodrigo. She wrote it for the soundtrack of The Hunger Games: The Ballad of Songbirds & Snakes (2023). Rodrigo wrote the song with its producer, Dan Nigro. Geffen Records released "Can't Catch Me Now" as the soundtrack album's second single on November 3, 2023. The song won the Hollywood Music in Media Award for Best Original Song in a Sci-Fi, Fantasy or Horror Film in 2023. ==References== Category:2023 songs Category:Olivia Rodrigo songs
